These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
Flower: zinnia, sunflower, bellflower, poppy
Pet: ferret, guinea-pig, hamster, rat
1. Pet:rat is not to the right of Pet:ferret##8
2. Pet:rat is on the right of Flower:zinnia##1
3. Flower:sunflower is on the left or right of Flower:bellflower##3
4. Flower:poppy is somewhere to the right of Pet:guinea-pig##5
5. Flower:poppy is not to the left of Pet:rat##8
6. Pet:hamster is somewhere to the left of Flower:sunflower##5
7. Flower:sunflower is somewhere between Flower:zinnia and Pet:guinea-pig##7
8. Flower:sunflower and Pet:rat have the same parity positions##9
9. Flower:bellflower and Pet:ferret have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | zinnia | sunflower | bellflower     | poppy |
| Pet           | hamster   | rat     | guinea-pig | ferret  |

