.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
Beverage: almond-milk, coffee, cola, tea
Birthday: march, july, september, october
1. Birthday:march is on the far left or far right##3
2. Birthday:october and Beverage:coffee have the same parity positions##9
3. Birthday:july is not to the right of Birthday:september##8
4. Birthday:march is not to the right of Beverage:tea##8
5. Birthday:march is somewhere to the left of Beverage:almond-milk##5
6. Beverage:almond-milk is somewhere to the right of Birthday:july##5
7. Beverage:coffee is somewhere to the right of Beverage:almond-milk##5
8. Beverage:tea is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | tea     | cola    | almond-milk | coffee    |
| Hobby      | march | july | september      | october |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
