2. Birthday:october is somewhere to the right of Beverage:fanta##5
3. Beverage:cola is on the left of Beverage:fanta##1
4. Beverage:cola is on the far left##1
5. Beverage:coffee is on the right of Beverage:fanta##1
6. Beverage:fanta is on the left of Birthday:october##1
7. Birthday:october is not to the left of Birthday:march##8
8. Beverage:cola and Birthday:march have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | cola    | fanta   | coffee    | milk  |
| Food       | march | november | october | june |

