.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
Job: coach, dressmaker, security-guard, software-developer
Sport: lacrosse, handball, badminton, biathlon
1. Sport:lacrosse == Job:dressmaker##1
2. Sport:handball is on the right of Sport:badminton##1
3. Sport:handball is somewhere to the left of Job:dressmaker##5
4. Sport:biathlon is on the left or right of Job:security-guard##3
5. Sport:handball is on the left of Job:coach##1
6. Job:software-developer and Sport:biathlon have the same parity positions##9
7. Job:security-guard is on the left or right of Job:coach##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | software-developer | security-guard | coach  | dressmaker |
| Music-Genre   | badminton             | handball          | biathlon | lacrosse    |

