.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-5::.
House: futuristic, colonial, townhouse, ranch-style
Pet: cat, dog, hedgehog, pony
1. House:townhouse != Pet:hedgehog##6
2. Pet:cat and House:futuristic have different parity positions##9
3. Pet:dog and House:colonial have different parity positions##9
4. Pet:dog is somewhere to the left of House:townhouse##5
5. Pet:cat is on the left of House:ranch-style##1
6. House:colonial != Pet:dog##6
7. House:ranch-style is somewhere to the left of House:colonial##5
8. Pet:cat is on the right of House:futuristic##1
9. Pet:pony != House:ranch-style##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | futuristic | townhouse | ranch-style  | colonial |
| Pet           | dog   | cat     | hedgehog | pony      |

