.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-20::.
Beverage: coffee, cola, juice, water
Movie-Genre: crime, romance, animation, scientific
 1. Beverage:water is on the left of Movie-Genre:crime##1
 2. Movie-Genre:animation is on the left of Movie-Genre:romance##1
 3. Movie-Genre:scientific is not to the right of Movie-Genre:animation##8
 4. Movie-Genre:romance is in an odd position##4
 5. Movie-Genre:crime != Beverage:cola##6
 6. Beverage:water is not to the right of Beverage:coffee##8
 7. Beverage:water and Movie-Genre:romance have the same parity positions##9
 8. Beverage:cola is not to the right of Beverage:juice##8
 9. Beverage:water == Movie-Genre:romance##1
10. Beverage:cola and Movie-Genre:romance have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | cola    | juice        | water   | coffee      |
| Hobby      | scientific | animation | romance | crime |

 